{"title":"Cant connect to MySQL server on localhost (10061)，数据库连接报错，无法远程连接","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.045Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/Cant connect to MySQL server on localhost (10061)，数据库连接报错，无法远程连接","updated":"2023-07-28T09:19:38.914Z","content":"<p>navicat连接数据总是报这个错，但是服务器防火墙端口权限、mysql远程连接都已经开启，本地也可以正常访问数据库。</p>\n<p>此时用<code>netstat -tunlp</code>查看一下网络端口，发现数据库的localAddress地址是127.0.0.1<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/12ca7d8dd3cf407ea439852fef0d5e11.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>需要修改数据库的配置文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#确认你的数据库配置文件路径对不对</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">vi /etc/mysql/my.cnf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>进去之后在<code>[mysql]</code>下面加上 <code>bind-address = 0.0.0.0</code><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/9880bd8bc08048e7b1b7c20518700044.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n然后按<code>esc</code>，输入<code>:wq</code>保存退出。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#重启mysql即可</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl restart mysql.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"docker安装elasticsearch","link":"2023/07/28/docker安装elasticsearch"},"next":{"title":"小米6刷机","link":"2023/07/28/小米6刷机"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/Cant connect to MySQL server on localhost (10061)，数据库连接报错，无法远程连接/","reading_time":"177 字约 1 分钟"}